data.title: Mennonite Archival Information Database
data.meta_description: William Hewat from Elmira, Ontario. Photo taken February 15, 1973. Hunsberger photo
data.text: David L. Hunsberger was the son of Noah and Minnie Hunsberger. Noah was the minister at Erb Street Mennonite Church for many years. When David was 14 they moved to St. Jacobs, where David lived for 55 years. In 1956 he married Katherine (Kate) Nafziger; they had three sons and one daughter. He was a professional photographer in the village for most of those years.
